# torrc — bad: ControlPort bound publicly with cookie auth only.
# The cookie file is local to the relay host, so a remote client
# cannot read it — but neither can it authenticate, which means
# the operator usually edits this further. As written today, it
# is a public unauthenticated control port.
SocksPort 9050
ControlPort 0.0.0.0:9051
CookieAuthentication 1
DataDirectory /var/lib/tor
